<script type="text/javascript" src="{{ 'jquery_accordion.js' | asset_url }}" async></script>
<div class="faq_container">
  <h1 class="faq_heading">FAQs</h1>
  <p class="faq_title">
    Got questions? Let's clear up your doubts; here are the most frequently asked questions to solve your queries.
  </p>
  <div class="faqpage">
    <div class="faq_ques" id="section1">Q. How long will it take to see results?<span></span></div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>
        The outcome is entirely dependent on the stage of your acne and the skin type you possess. Take our quiz to
        evaluate your acne stage & the best regime to win the battle against it,
        <a href="https://www.acnesquad.com/pages/quiz-intro">Click Here</a>
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq_ques" id="section2">Q. When should I use these products?<span></span></div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>
        If you have acne-prone skin, generally sensitive skin or any other skin type that aspires to have clear and
        healthy skin, Acne Squad range is perfect for you. We recommend you take our quiz to understand your skin and
        its needs better. <a href="https://www.acnesquad.com/pages/quiz-intro">Click Here</a>
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq_ques" id="section3">Q. Will this suit my sensitive skin?<span></span></div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>
        Yes, our products have been co-created with dermatologists and are non-comedogenic (don't block/clog pores).
        They will be kind to your skin but not to your acne.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript">
  $(document).ready(function() {
  $('.faq_ques').accordion({
  cookieName: 'accordion_nav'
  });
  });
</script>
<style>
  .faq_container {
        margin: 0 151px;
        padding: 50px;
      }
      .faq_heading {
        text-align: center;
        color: #a99ef6;
        font-size: 50px;
        line-height: 42px;
        font-family: BebasNeue;
      }

      .faq_title {
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        text-align: center;
        color: #707070;
        font-family: Europa_Regular;
        font-size: 15px;
        line-height: 1.3;
      }

      .accordion-open span {
        display: block;
        position: absolute;
        right: 3px;
        top: 25%;
        padding: 16px;
        background:url('{{ 'down.png' | asset_img_url }}') center center no-repeat;
        background-size: 40% 40%;
      }
      .accordion-close span {
        display: block;
        position: absolute;
        right: 3px;
        top: 25%;
        padding: 16px;
        background:url('{{ 'greater.png' | asset_img_url }}') center center no-repeat;
        background-size: 40% 40%;
      }

      .faqpage {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .faq_ques {
        padding: 1rem 1rem 1rem 0;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #464545;
        font-size: 1em;
        width: 100%;
        position: relative;
        cursor: pointer;
      }

      .faq_container .faqpage .content {
        font-size: 0.9em;
        color: #464545;
        line-height: 1.5em;
        font-size: 15px;
        padding: 0 1rem 0 0;
        font-family: Europa_Regular;
        line-height: 1.3;
        border-bottom: 2px solid #474646;
        margin-top: -1px;
      }
      .faq_container .faqpage .content p a {
        text-decoration: underline;
        color: #464545;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 0.9em;
      }
</style>

